h1. {anchor:about-life-the-universe-computers-and-everything}About [Life|http://norvig.com/quotations.html#life], [The Universe|http://norvig.com/quotations.html#universe], [Computers,|http://norvig.com/quotations.html#computers] and [Everything|http://norvig.com/quotations.html#everything]

